Shortly after 7pm on Monday night, 30 members of the EFF invaded the sprawling farmhouse of Gonubie killer Fritz Joubert. The Fighters said the occupation was a show of force against racism. Joubert, 45, killed sangoma Anele Hoyana at the weekend after filming long rants where he claimed to be the chosen one and accused Hoyana, who he later bludgeoned to death, of being satan. Joubert was later shot dead while attacking a police officer. Read more in tomorrow's Daily Dispatch and on DispatchLIVE.